4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:18,000
Studies show that sodium and potassium are key players in this process.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:21,600
Research indicates that optimal electrolyte levels enhance cognitive function.

6
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:26,000
Stay hydrated and keep your electrolytes balanced for peak brain performance!

